subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Curt Hocker, an Illinois amateur, recorded five holes in one over the last week, including two on the same day at El Paso Golf Club in Kappa, Ill. This year, Hocker, 22, has seven aces, five on par-4s, and two double eagles.
